    This elemenet represents an Autosar EcuExtract. The EcuExtract is used by the RTE Editor to identify SW Components and the ECUInstance that map to the ECU that hosts the RTE. The EcuExtract is a toplevel singleton. If present the SystemModel is to be interpreted as an EcuExtract for the referenced ECU.
